===Noun===
'''compartment'''
#A [[room]], or [[section]], or [[chamber]]
#:*''"Two men were seated in a [[well-lighted]] [[compartment]] of a [[third-class]] [[carriage]]."''
#One of the [[part]]s in which an [[area]] is [[subdivided]].

